%% MCP Integration - Notion Connection via Model Context Protocol
%% Shows how Project Manager connects to Notion API

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as 🎬 Creative Director
    participant PM as 📋 Project Manager<br/>(ADK Agent)
    participant MCP as 🔌 McpToolset<br/>(ADK MCP Integration)
    participant NPX as 📦 npx Process<br/>(Node.js)
    participant NotionMCP as 🖥️ @notionhq/notion-mcp-server<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant NotionAPI as 📝 Notion API

    Note over Orchestrator: Campaign complete,<br/>need timeline

    Orchestrator->>PM: Create project timeline<br/>(Campaign details via A2A)

    Note over PM: Agent receives task

    PM->>PM: Determine need for<br/>schema discovery

    rect rgb(66, 133, 244)
    Note over PM,NotionAPI: 🔍 DYNAMIC SCHEMA DISCOVERY

    PM->>MCP: Use tool: API-retrieve-a-database<br/>(Projects DB ID)

    MCP->>NPX: Start MCP server if needed<br/>npx -y @notionhq/notion-mcp-server

    NPX->>NotionMCP: Launch server<br/>(Stdio transport)

    NotionMCP->>NotionAPI: GET /v1/databases/{id}

    NotionAPI->>NotionMCP: Database schema:<br/>- Properties<br/>- Types<br/>- Options

    NotionMCP->>MCP: Return schema via MCP protocol

    MCP->>PM: Schema information

    Note over PM: Adapt to actual schema<br/>No hardcoded property names!
    end

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    Note over PM,NotionAPI: ✏️ CREATE PROJECT PAGE

    PM->>MCP: Use tool: API-post-page<br/>(Projects DB, page content)

    MCP->>NotionMCP: MCP request

    NotionMCP->>NotionAPI: POST /v1/pages<br/>(Create project page)

    NotionAPI->>NotionMCP: Project page created<br/>(page_id)

    NotionMCP->>MCP: Success response

    MCP->>PM: Project page ID
    end

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    Note over PM,NotionAPI: 📝 CREATE TASK PAGES

    loop For each task (5-10 tasks)
        PM->>MCP: Use tool: API-post-page<br/>(Tasks DB, task content + project relation)

        MCP->>NotionMCP: MCP request

        NotionMCP->>NotionAPI: POST /v1/pages<br/>(Create task, link to project)

        NotionAPI->>NotionMCP: Task page created

        NotionMCP->>MCP: Success response

        MCP->>PM: Task created
    end
    end

    Note over PM: Generate text timeline<br/>+ Notion links

    PM->>Orchestrator: ✅ Timeline complete:<br/>• Text-based timeline<br/>• Project page link<br/>• Task page links

    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Present to user

    rect rgb(251, 188, 4)
    Note over PM,NotionAPI: 🔑 KEY INNOVATIONS:<br/>• Dynamic schema discovery<br/>• Multilingual support<br/>• No hardcoded properties<br/>• Two-database architecture<br/>• Stdio MCP transport
    end
